      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>PUGLIA--Giacomo. June 6th, 2007, at age 78. Cherished husband of Felice (nee Ochs). Beloved father of Howard and Marianne, father-in-law of Gina, and grandfather of Zackary and Elizabeth. Leaves behind his devoted family in Italy. A wonderful man who embraced life and lived it to the fullest.</p>
      </block>
